# Finances

Loaded only when a financial question arises. Not surfaced in casual briefings.

> **Sensitivity warning:** This file may end up containing your net worth, account balances, holdings, and tax situation. The `.gitignore` for this repo excludes the `memory/` directory by default — keep it that way. If you fork publicly, double-check before you push.

> **How to populate:** Fill in the sections that apply to you. Skip the rest. The monthly financial sweep briefing reads this to compute deltas.

